Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞 瑪麗亞在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易達阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燉小腿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心多做了呢 就想分給你些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 這是怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是嬰兒的撥浪鼓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰給的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威利 過來幫我搬東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…個 少爺的內褲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中 上次的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 萬事都按少爺的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經做好在那裏住宿的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 少爺 我們去哪旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連那種事都不知道還來捆行李嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個執事 解約
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王殿下應該是在大約在三天前到達了巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在視察萬博會的會場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必酒店的警戒應該很嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的心不在這裏對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劉說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下要挑起歐洲的…不…世界的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是去覲見女王的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為那個叫阿巴萊恩特的人的死感到悲傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個棋子無視了我的命令 煩人地幹涉進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劉也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不把握住棋子的意圖和戰力的話 是玩不成遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從埃菲爾塔入場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰神廣場的會場裏美術宮和各個展覽館林立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從鐵道運來的大量的貨物 凝聚了藝術的精華的機械展館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特羅卡迪羅廣場是農業展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第二會場榮軍院廣場裏正在舉行殖民地博覽會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其內容為古代遺跡的重建 民族工業 人類 動物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與往年不同的是從美國來的牛仔的野性秀還有失常工業之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的萬博會 也為了新商品的開發 再稍微四處轉轉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 驚奇宮裏好像有天使的標本出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是值得一看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的標本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽啊 只不過是猴子而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中生存下來的您的話 這點程度的黑暗根本不算什麽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺請去會場外面避難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中奔跑一點也不難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的靈魂一直在黑暗中奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏真的是我生活的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 這麽慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾 好久不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在新世紀之前 將歐洲改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏在溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏在沈澱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏有汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有將全部破壞一次的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不破壞就沒有創造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了迎接潔凈的新世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我國將吹起席卷一切的風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法多姆海恩府是我凈化的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麽的惡趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…這裏\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倫敦大橋正在倒下來 倒下來 倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倫敦大橋正在倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我美麗的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓您告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽不僅僅是殺掉 還要制造出那麽悲慘的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能將危險放置一旁不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾 那是凈化哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕蔑死者是您所謂的凈化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輕蔑了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕蔑 我… 對一直以來對我盡忠的法多姆海恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您吃驚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像是散發著年輕氣息的少女一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下在幸福的半途中失去了心愛的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下哀傷著夫君的死 曾一度也想了解自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「為了能與心愛的夫君一起永遠的一起生活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將陛下的身體與夫君的身體連在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫君理解我做出的行動 並對此感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣夫君的身體就…怦怦地在跳著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怦怦 生命的躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與相愛的人一起成為真實的意義那種喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想贈與法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其死決不會成為淒慘之物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麽想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下與夫君擁有將英國指引向純凈的強烈的意誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其誌向將自己的汙穢一掃而光 成為了這樣純潔的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麽崇高的誌向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與月下的天使正相配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使？難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞修 至少讓夏爾在你的刀刃下終結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞修的刀刃是非常美麗的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像沐浴在新世紀的朝日光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對著智慧的榮耀拔出劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將你體內的野獸拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把他推進深淵裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願你有純白色的來世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾·法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是自己擅長的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊不中的話也是沒有意義的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許這就是終點了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽 請下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將亞修…殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅有這些…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將女王…殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麽荒唐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓這個東西停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓別人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 只會增加騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是普通的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽要在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就此撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽讓我停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會引人註目 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的願望是對讓自己落入地獄的人復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日的誓言是怎麽說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您將我喚醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個事實永遠不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經付出的代價永遠不會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽 選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將成為您的劍 幫您完成復仇的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其代價為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂什麽的 不論多少都讓你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日的您應該沒有猶豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道了事實 還要向女王盡忠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從一開始就沒有對她的忠誠心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是作為法多姆海恩家的主人行動罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽 靈魂真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂什麽的怎麽可能有 真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好像累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了驛館後 請好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人討厭的累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天開始 取掉了我的襯衫的紐扣的你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過讓惡魔來模仿執事的工作 你還做的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為法多姆海恩家的執事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話就到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該休息了 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請忘記一切 願您有個幸福的美夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有再一次獲得未來的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍棄女王的看門狗這一稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍棄一直懷抱的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯…蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安 去哪了 早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不到我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是702室的法多姆海恩 隨從去哪了知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印記沒有消失 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請忘記一切 願您有個幸福的美夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家夥才不會希望我有什麽幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 「忘記一切」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訣別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到倫敦之類的事 我自己一人也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將我帶到加萊的港口去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 小子 那是拜托別人的態度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該說去是加萊的港口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思呢 不巧我家是反方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布洛涅港口的話 就往反方向一直走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正 慢慢地拐來拐去的話 遲早會到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你這家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出和我給你的代價相應的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一晚 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了倫敦再補寄給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麽玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是誰嗎 夏爾·法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪的小販
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道法多姆海恩公司嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個指環 是法多姆海恩代代相傳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽就這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那個指環做代價就讓你住下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺不錯的石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐也給你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麽玩笑 區區一個便宜旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 來這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵 連你也耍本少爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麽近的地方…有港口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使這樣我也 那樣仿徨著 沒有找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明…在如此近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水…水…去拿水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
